OL,3,CMartha's rule is having a
OL,4,Ctransformative effect on patient care
OL,5,Cin the NHS
OL,7,FMartha's Rule, which gives patients
OL,8,Fand their loved ones the right to a
OL,9,Fsecond medical opinion, can "save
OL,10,Flives", Martha Mills's mother has said.
OL,12,FThe new second medical opinion scheme
OL,13,Fhas also been welcomed by Labour and
OL,14,FConservative MPs.
OL,16,FThe first two months of the initiative
OL,17,Fsaw 14 people transferred to intensive
OL,18,Fcare units after patients, their
OL,19,Ffamily or NHS staff called for a
OL,20,Fsecond opinion.
