OL,7,FOther patients have also been moved to
OL,8,Fhigh-dependency units, coronary care
OL,9,Funits and received other care, such as
OL,10,Freturning to operating theatres.
OL,12,FMerope Mills lost her daughter Martha,
OL,13,F13, to sepsis in 2021 after she was
OL,14,Fadmitted to King's College Hospital,
OL,15,Fin south London, after injuring her
OL,16,Fpancreas in a cycling accident.
