OL,7,FMartha's Rule serves as an escalation
OL,8,Fprocess and offers patients and
OL,9,Ffamilies the power to seek a second
OL,10,Fopinion if they believe a patient's
OL,11,Fcondition is deteriorating and they
OL,12,Fare not being listened to.
