OL,3,CMartha's rule is having a
OL,4,Ctransformative effect on patient care
OL,5,Cin the NHS
OL,7,F"So pushing through this change has
OL,8,Fbeen exhausting at times but in some
OL,9,Flevel it has helped us both to see
OL,10,Fthat people are prepared to learn from
OL,11,FMartha's death and those mistakes.
OL,13,F"It's clear to me that if we implement
OL,14,FMartha's Rule nationally, we can
OL,15,Fconfidently say that it would greatly
OL,16,Fimprove care, change the culture and
OL,17,Fsave lives."
