OL,7,F"I'd really like it to be simple
OL,8,Faround the country and for patients to
OL,9,Funderstand it in the way that they
OL,10,Funderstand 999 and 111."
OL,12,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said
OL,13,FMartha's Rule is helping to "build a
OL,14,Fsafer NHS" while NHS England said its
OL,15,Fintroduction had been "one of the
OL,16,Fimportant changes to patient care in
OL,17,Frecent years".
