OL,3,CMartha's rule is having a
OL,4,Ctransformative effect on patient care
OL,5,Cin the NHS
OL,7,F"The rollout of Martha's Rule is
OL,8,Falready playing a role in building a
OL,9,Fsafer NHS by putting patients and
OL,10,Ftheir families at the heart of
OL,11,Fdiscussions about their healthcare,
OL,12,Fand early indications are that it
OL,13,Fcould have a transformative impact."
OL,15,FFormer health secretary Jeremy Hunt
OL,16,Fhas said that Mr Streeting should
OL,17,Fmandate Martha's Rule across NHS
OL,18,Fhospitals in England.
