OL,3,CMartha's rule is having a
OL,4,Ctransformative effect on patient care
OL,5,Cin the NHS
OL,7,FProfessor Sir Stephen Powis, national
OL,8,Fmedical director for the NHS in
OL,9,FEngland, said: "The introduction of
OL,10,FMartha's Rule represents one of the
OL,11,Fmost important changes to patient care
OL,12,Fin recent years, and we are really
OL,13,Fencouraged to see the impact it is
OL,14,Falready having for patients in this
OL,15,Ffirst phase.
OL,17,F"This early data highlights just how
OL,18,Fessential the Martha's Rule escalation
OL,19,Fprocess will be for patients, families
OL,20,Fand staff."
