OL,5,Cin the NHS
OL,7,FThe pilot scheme of Martha's Rule will
OL,8,Fend in 2025. An evaluation of the
OL,9,Fpilot will inform proposals for it to
OL,10,Fbe rolled out to the final 65
OL,11,Fhospitals in England not currently
OL,12,Fparticipating.
OL,14,FThe evaluation could also propose that
OL,15,Fthe scheme is expanded beyond
OL,16,Fhospitals to other healthcare settings.
